    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell functions as @Compendium[pf1.spells.vqfrp8t0c1lw1jna]{Heroism}, except that you can reverse the spell by issuing a special command as a standard action if you are within medium range (100 feet + 10 feet per caster level) of the target. The target loses the bonuses and instead takes a -2 penalty on attack rolls, saving throws, and skill checks until the spell's duration ends (no save). Attempts to identify hollow <em>heroism</em> with a skill check incorrectly identify it as <em>heroism</em> (see the ruse descriptor on page 192).</p>",
